• Community Health Systems has reached full virtualization of its server environment using VMWare technologies.
• In 2012, Community Health Systems, Inc. called off its planned implementation of AllScripts Electronic Health Records System. Instead, IT and medical executives decided to install the Athena Clinical EHR platform from athenahealth, due in part to the Meaningful use Considerations.





